lead_paragraph: A month ago, Carlos Rodon was deep into a disappointing season. However, the 23-year-old left-hander now is in the midst of a major turnaround.

headline.print_headline: Rodon, Morneau, Cabrera Lead White Sox Past Mariners, 4-1
